notes: Beautifully renovated modern apartment with custom built-in cabinetry, recessed lighting, and high-quality finishes throughout. The space appears very clean with smooth tile floors and rounded furniture edges that are relatively baby-friendly, though the glass display cabinet and small decorative items on shelves would need childproofing. Natural light appears limited based on heavy curtains, but artificial lighting is excellent; at 5F/13F this building almost certainly has an elevator.
